image_analysis.description: A color photograph showing two actors, a woman and a man, posing with Oscar statuettes. The woman, Lupita Nyong'o, is on the left wearing a light blue gown and holding her award. The man, Jared Leto, is next to her, wearing a white tuxedo jacket and black pants, also holding his award with a joyful expression. To their right is a large, oversized Oscar statue. The base of the large statue is surrounded by colorful flowers. Text is overlaid at the bottom of the image.
